4 (2) ENSURE THAT A COPY OF THE CLINICAL STAFFING PLAN IS
5 AVAILABLE, ON REQUEST, ON EACH PATIENT UNIT; AND
6 (3) POST THE CLINICAL STAFFING PLAN ON THE HOSPITAL’S
7 WEBSITE.
8 (B) IF A CLINICAL STAFFING PLAN FOR A UNIT IS AMENDED AFTER IT IS
9 IMPLEMENTED, THE HOSPITAL SHALL POST OR PROVIDE THE AMENDED CLINICAL
10 STAFFING PLAN FOR THE UNIT IN THE MANNER REQUIRED UNDER SUBSECTION (A)
11 OF THIS SECTION, IN A TIMELY MANNER.
12 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That each hospital shall establish
13 a clinical staffing committee as required under § 19–388 of the Health – General Article,
14 as enacted by Section 1 of this Act, on or before January 1, 2026.
15 SECTION 3. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That each clinical staffing
16 committee shall develop a clinical staffing plan as required under § 19–388 of the
17 Health – General Article, as enacted by Section 1 of this Act, on or before July 1, 2026.
18 SECTION 4. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
19 October 1, 2025.

